DECAY-DATA (75-RE-178,13.2MIN,DG,237.,0.447)
COMMENT    - By authors. The experiment shows that the rhenium
           products are formed only by deexcitation of the
           compound nucleus, Re-181, in complete fusion reaction.
MISC-COL   (MISC) The fitted data obtained using PACE2 code.
