REACTION   (69-TM-169(6-C-12,X)71-LU-172-G,M+,SIG)
DECAY-DATA (71-LU-172-G,6.7D,DG,1093.6,0.624)
COMMENT    - By compiler. Lu-172 production due to Hf-172 decay is
           negligible, because half-life of Hf-172 is equal 1.87
           years.
           - By authors. The calculated cross section is
           negligible compared to experimental data. This shows
           that 172-Lu and 171-Lu are formed purely by incomplete
           fusion reaction such as 169-Tm(C-12,Be-8)173-Lu.
HISTORY    (20260202A) SD: SF5=IND/M+ -> M+ in RREACTION code.
ENDBIB              10
