BIB                  4         11
REACTION   (69-TM-169(6-C-12,FUS),,SIG)
COMMENT    - By authors. The total complete fusion cross section
           was obtained by adding complete fusion cross sections
           of all products.  The cross section includes the
           unmeasured complete fusion cross section of W-177,
           which constitutes about 1.5% of the total fusion cross
           section.
MISC-COL   (MISC) Incomplete fusion cross section
           (MISC-ERR) The uncertainty of "MISC".
